## 6. MVP SCOPE

| Element | In MVP |
|---|---|
| Markets | Match Winner 1X2 · Total Goals · Asian Handicap |
| Events | Goal · Red Card · VAR overturn · Finalization |
| Execution | Simulated devnet order book |
| Chain | Solana devnet receipts |
| Demo | 1 match, 3 markets, 1 strong event shock |

**NOT in MVP:** Real-money betting, token/NFT, social features, 12+ agents, heavy ML pipeline, LLM as decision-maker (LLM = explanation only)

---

## 7. TECH STACK

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Core engine | Python (asyncio + websockets) |
| Feed | TxLINE SSE (live) + recorded replay (demo safety) |
| On-chain | TxLINE Anchor validation + RAVEN Solana Memo receipts |
| Verification | TypeScript (`verify.ts`) |
| Dashboard | All-black terminal + minimal web frontend |
| Explanation | Deterministic decision rationale emitted by the Risk Kernel |
| Bonus | `@txline/sdk` open-source ingestion package |

---

## 8. DATA MODEL

### TxLINE Input (normalized)
```json
{
  "fixture_id": 17952170,
  "match_time": "67:14",
  "score": {"home": 1, "away": 0},
  "odds": {"home": 1.72, "draw": 3.60, "away": 5.40},
  "event_type": "PENALTY_AWARDED",
  "sequence": 428,
  "status_id": 6,
  "period": 2
}
```

### Finalization Detection
Per TxLINE conventions: `game_finalised` event OR `statusId=100` OR `period=100`

