## 9. NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS

| ID | Requirement | Target |
|---|---|---|
| NFR1 | Event-to-withdrawal ordering | Same decision tick; no shock-frame fill |
| NFR2 | Determinism | Same input → same output, 100% |
| NFR3 | Judge testability | No token purchase / deposit required |
| NFR4 | Replay uptime | Runs flawlessly during review week (July 19–29) |
| NFR5 | Code clarity | Every formula documented, clean architecture |
| NFR6 | Data compliance | No raw TxLINE data redistribution |
| NFR7 | Branding | No FIFA marks / official sponsor imagery |

